Class StartUI

  • java.lang.Object
    • javafx.application.Application
      • UI.UI
        • UI.StartUI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DisplayIF

    public class StartUI
extends UI
    UI used to start the client application. It contains everything related to this stage. It the starts UIs according to the information received from the server.
